LEGISLATIVE CONTENT (DATA)
public domain (work of the U.S. Government, 17 U.S.C. § 105)
These are official public-sector texts reproduced from their official
source. The original source of each document is recorded in the `source`
field of that file's YAML front matter.

DISCLAIMER
Automated reproduction of official sources. This is not an official or
verified legal text. Always consult the official source for authoritative
versions.
